sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI
    participant APIGateway as API Gateway
    participant BFF as Campaign BFF
    participant Orch as Campaign Submission Orchestrator
    participant Participants as Participants Service
    participant Campaign as Campaign Service
    participant Cache as Cache Store
    participant SAPHRMS as SAP HRMS
    participant AdapterService as Adapter Service
    participant DistList as PostgreSQL Distribution List

    Note over Cache,DistList: Daily cache refresh runs for users and distribution lists

    User->>UI: Add users to campaign
    UI->>APIGateway: Request to add users
    APIGateway->>BFF: Forward request
    BFF->>Orch: Initiate campaign submission
    
    Orch->>Participants: Request user details
    Participants->>Cache: Fetch user names
    
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>Participants: Return cached user data
    else Cache Miss
        Participants->>APIGateway: Request user data from SAP
        APIGateway->>APIGateway: Validate SAP service key
        
        alt Valid Service Key
            APIGateway->>AdapterService: Forward SAP request
            AdapterService->>SAPHRMS: Fetch user data
            SAPHRMS-->>AdapterService: Return user data
            AdapterService-->>APIGateway: Return user data
            APIGateway-->>Participants: Return user data
            Participants->>Cache: Store user data in cache
        else Invalid Service Key
            APIGateway-->>Participants: Authentication failed
        end
    end
    
    Participants->>DistList: Fetch distribution list data
    
    alt DL Cache Hit
        DistList->>Cache: Check DL cache
        Cache-->>DistList: Return cached DL data
        DistList-->>Participants: Return DL data
    else DL Cache Miss
        DistList-->>Participants: Return DL data from DB
        Participants->>Cache: Store DL data in cache
    end
    
    Participants-->>Orch: Return user and DL details
    Orch->>Campaign: Update campaign with users
    Campaign-->>Orch: Campaign updated
    Orch-->>BFF: Success response
    BFF-->>APIGateway: Success response
    APIGateway-->>UI: Success response
    UI-->>User: Users added successfully

    Note over Cache: Cache refreshed daily for users and distribution lists